    <description>Enterprise Evidence &amp; Document Intelligence (Program 024C): structured, traceable, confidence-scored intelligence extracted from a document. Points to the actual file in Salesforce Files (ContentDocument) — never duplicates storage. Links evidence to Opportunity Signal / Company Profile / Acquisition Source so every recommendation is traceable to source+document+confidence. AI summarizes evidence; it never replaces it.</description>
